{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "23dfa63d-d820-429a-99a4-221b6194599b", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/23dfa63d-d820-429a-99a4-221b6194599b@1.pkg/1772597612791/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597613665", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/23dfa63d-d820-429a-99a4-221b6194599b@1.pkg/1772597612791/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597613665"}, "identifier": "23dfa63d-d820-429a-99a4-221b6194599b", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>C：DeepSeek、“秧BOY”、“人造太阳”等都是中国式现代化建设中取得的伟大成就，这些成就让青少年拥有坚定的民族自信，体现了自信源于此，故C符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>A：材料中体现的民族自信源于国家发展成就，而非和他人交往中的肯定和认同，故A不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>B：题干强调的是祖国高质量发展带来的自信，并非青少年自身积累的实力，故B不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>D：青少年的责任感是自信的表现或影响因素，并非材料中自信的来源，故D不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>故本题选C。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>2025年开年,DeepSeek惊艳世界,“秧BOY”舞动春晚,“人造太阳”刷新纪录……作为新时代的青少年，我们见证了祖国的高质量发展，拥有了坚定的民族自信。材料所体现的自信源于（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "2025年开年,DeepSeek惊艳世界,“秧BOY”舞动春晚,“人造太阳”刷新纪录……作为新时代的青少年，我们见证了祖国的高质量发展，拥有了坚定的民族自信。材料所体现的自信源于（   ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/23dfa63d-d820-429a-99a4-221b6194599b@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755100132888", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_ans